I’ve isolated the required rewrite. The fix is not just a compile tweak: the PoC assumed `provider == COMPOUND`, but the vault prices all lender balances together, so stale cUSDT can still dilute deposits while Aave is the active provider. I’m replacing the funding path with a UniswapV2/Sushi-style flashswap and removing that incorrect gate.
